description: This traybake makes for a fantastic fakeaway dish served with rice or noodles.
name: Asian Inspired Sticky Chicken Traybake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Divide the vegetables between 4 plates ensuring each has an orange wedge for squeezing over. Top each with a sticky chicken leg and serve with rice, if desired.
